    <section class=" flex flex-col w-2/3  lg:text-center mb-4">
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <p class=" italic font-thin">Last updated: 02/07/2025</p>
            <p>Charles Lindecker ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <div>
                    <p class=" font-semibold">We may collect the following types of personal data:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc lg:list-none pl-6 dark:marker:text-white">
                        <li><span class=" font-bold">Identity Data</span>: name, email address</li>
                        <li><span class=" font-bold">Contact Data</span>: email address, IP address</li>
                        <li><span class=" font-bold">Technical Data</span>: browser type, operating system, device type, and browsing actions</li>
                        <li><span class=" font-bold">Usage Data</span>: pages visited, time spent, interaction data</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class=" mt-4">
                    <p class=" font-semibold">We collect this data when:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc lg:list-none pl-6 dark:marker:text-white">
                        <li>You fill out a form</li>
                        <li>You register or log in</li>
                        <li>You interact with our website (analytics, cookies)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 2. Use of Your Information</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <div>
                    <p class=" font-semibold">We use your information to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc lg:list-none pl-6 dark:marker:text-white">
                        <li>Provide and maintain the website</li>
                        <li>Respond to your inquiries or requests</li>
                        <li>Ensure security and prevent fraud</li>
                        <li>Improve user experience and site functionality</li>
                        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 3. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <div>
                    <p class=" font-semibold">If you are in the European Economic Area, our legal bases include:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc lg:list-none pl-6 dark:marker:text-white">
                        <li>Your consent</li>
                        <li>Performance of a contract</li>
                        <li>Legal obligation</li>
                        <li>Legitimate interests</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 4. Sharing of Information</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <div>
                    <p class=" font-semibold">We do not sell your personal data. However, we may share it with:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc lg:list-none pl-6 dark:marker:text-white">
                        <li>Service providers for website hosting, analytics, email services</li>
                        <li>Legal authorities if required by law</li>
                        <li>Third-party open source services if integrated and necessary</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 5. Data Retention</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <p>We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, including legal or reporting obligations.</p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 6. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <div>
                    <p class=" font-semibold">You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc lg:list-none pl-6 dark:marker:text-white">
                        <li>Access, correct or delete your data</li>
                        <li>Withdraw your consent at any time</li>
                        <li>Request data portability</li>
                        <li>Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at: [not define]</p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 7. Cookies</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <p>We use cookies to enhance user experience, perform analytics, and maintain website security. You can manage or disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
                <p>See our <a href="#" target="_blank" class=" text-blue-500">Cookie Policy</a> for more details.</p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 8. Security</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <p>We implement technical and organizational measures to protect your data, including HTTPS encryption, firewalls, and regular audits.</p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. All changes will be posted on this page with the updated revision date.</p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class=" flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
            <h2 class=" font-bold text-2xl ml-2"> 10. Contact </h2>
            <div class=" flex flex-col gap-1">
                <p class=" font-semibold">For any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data:</p>
                <p>Charles Lindecker</p>
                <p>Email: <a href="mailto:charles.lindecker@outlook.fr" target="_blank" class=" text-blue-500 underline">charles.lindecker@outlook.fr</a></p>
            </div>
        </article>
